{"tid":1304721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼《花木蘭》爸像習近平  劉亦菲畫華為妝","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:17:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8e725c39f0182015b92ba0c559d8b868301858","tid":1304721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/7-10/p2465511a446460645-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F7-10%2Fp2465511a446460645-ss.jpg&h=3cbb3d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真人版電影《花木蘭》（網路圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n木蘭父「好像習近平」<br />\n<br />\n預告片中最吸引網友的是飾演木蘭父親的演員，因為長相極像習近平，讓網友掀起一陣討論，調侃說「看了幾遍，確認是習總」、「原來木蘭她爸是習近平」 、「超像」。<br />\n<br />\n劉亦菲畫「華為妝」老外看不懂<br />\n<br />\n最有趣的是，國內、海外觀眾對真人版電影《花木蘭》的反應與討論焦點大不同。<br />\n<br />\n他們疑惑，為什麼花木蘭要把華為的Logo畫在額頭上？這讓劉亦菲原本淡雅精緻的面容，變成「人體彩繪」；也許多網友戲稱這簡直就是「華為妝」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有人解釋說，此妝容正好符合《木蘭辭》中的描寫的「當窗理雲鬢，對鏡貼花黃。」還原了魏晉南北朝時期女子的妝容。<br />\n<br />\n「花木蘭」真人版預計2020年春季上映，故事講述皇帝有一天突然下令，每一戶人家都必須要有一名男丁加入軍隊，一起抵抗北方入侵的外族。花木蘭身為長女，毅然決定替父從軍。她換上男裝，用了男人的名字成功混入軍中，一路屢建戰功，讓家族引以為傲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/07/10/899892.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F899892.html&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3UYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a988ca43\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/07/10/899892.html</a>"},{"pid":"231d78702a6ec22e44740c946758c43c9cb581dc","tid":1304721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0ef64b9479d5e2a7ce623404dadf18d3806657","tid":1304721,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:11:19.000Z","msg":"個妝仲衰撚過呀梅"},{"pid":"28828d70698895dae7a64424a64fe8641b6a9c99","tid":1304721,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd3963ec5dbe764ece2b9cdc177ecc72c9cfe3c","tid":1304721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/public/uploads/assets/2019/07/10/2019-07-10-5d25e67432c39-780x408-300157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F2019-07-10-5d25e67432c39-780x408-300157.jpg&h=03789c8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a607bd3ea7186592727595473b2b0bac2da290e9","tid":1304721,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲搞什麼"}]}